            <title>[FLINK-2353] Hadoop mapred IOFormat wrappers do not respect JobConfigurable interface </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2353</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hadoop&apos;s mapred API features the &lt;tt&gt;JobConfigurable&lt;/tt&gt; interface which offers a function &lt;tt&gt;configure(JobConf)&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;to configure user-defined classes such as InputFormats, OutputFormats, and InputSplits.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Flink&apos;s Hadoop compatibility wrappers do not respect this interface.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
